<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/302178-i-love-this-book-i-watched-the-movie-then">I love this book! I watched the movie then read the book after my former teacher, Joe, lent me it. I didn&#39;t know there was a book until he lent it to me! Once I read that book, I had to read more and so now I&#39;ve read the whole series. Diana is a great author (and creates great, clever women) :D . One question I have is why would Sophie in the movie have brown hair when she really has RED hair in the book?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
